data.description: This spacious 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is located in the desirable Lakewood Estates. With recent updates and upgrades, this home is ready for its new owners. One of the standout features of this property is the new sewer lines that were installed in 2022, ensuring worry-free and efficient plumbing for years to come. Additionally, a tankless hot water heater was installed in 2020, offering endless hot water and energy savings.The roof and AC were replaced in 2018, providing peace of mind and energy efficiency. The front door was recently replaced, adding both curb appeal and security to the home. Inside, you'll find a Samsung washer and dryer, making laundry tasks a breeze. The entire interior has been freshly painted, creating a clean and inviting atmosphere.Step outside and enjoy the large fenced yard, perfect for pets or outdoor activities. The vinyl fencing was replaced just 2 years ago, adding both functionality and beauty to the outdoor space. A standout feature of this property is the workshop in the backyard, complete with electricity. Whether you're a hobbyist or need extra storage space, this workshop offers endless possibilities. Location is key, and this home has it all. Just 10 minutes from downtown, you'll have quick and easy access to all the amenities and attractions the city has to offer. Additionally, you'll be only 20 minutes away from Palmetto and Parish, providing convenient access to even more shopping, entertainment, and dining options. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a well-maintained and updated home in Lakewood Estates. Schedule a showing today and make this house your home.
